Week 1: Project Introduction & Data Understanding,Selection.
Objective: Understand Problem Statement And Explore Dataset.
In the first week of this internship, the Problem Statement of the project was clearly understood and explain what exactly we have to do .
The project focuses on optimizing IT support team performance using data analytics and visualization tools.
Different datasets related to IT support tickets and helpdesk systems were explored from Kaggle and other online sources.
After evaluating several options, a suitable IT support ticket dataset was selected for the project.
The dataset includes information such as ticket ID, issue category, priority level, ticket status, and resolution time. Understanding the project scope and selecting the appropriate dataset were the main goals of this week.
  
